  cardDescription: First-class researcher and alchemist, she was recruited to use
    an ancient spell that would have put an end to the war. Not trusting the tome,
    she refused to take part in it. Her memories were blurry. She used to wake up
    at night, remembering different outcomes of that war, and wrote all her notes
    in a diary.
